00:55:47.900 --> 00:55:53.760
at very specific development
interest in the form

00:55:53.760 --> 00:55:57.320
of mokuhanga appropriating
some traditional techniques

00:55:57.320 --> 00:56:00.490
in North America, artists,
contemporary artists

00:56:00.490 --> 00:56:01.790
who are using these forms.

00:56:01.790 --> 00:56:07.550
And it's a beautiful book
to look at, the latter half

00:56:07.550 --> 00:56:10.520
of the book are images
of 50 odd artists

00:56:10.520 --> 00:56:11.870
who are working in these modes.

00:56:11.870 --> 00:56:14.830
So that's a whole
another dimension of this.

00:56:14.830 --> 00:56:17.760
And there is some exchange
